item.description: If you are interested in hearing myself and Dr. Anthony Catalano share how you can Change your Thoughts, in order to Change your life, come and join us. Any questions feel free to call me on my cell: 603-490-4371. Looking forward to meeting you. Absolutely invite a friend to join you but you must RSVP as there is very limited seating. You can get there between 6:30 and 6:45 as we will start promptly at 7pm. See you there!
item.how_to_find_us: Go in the front door and ask for the meeting room for the ENRICHMENT GROUP. It is to the left of the building.
item.why: This is a unique opportunity to hear Dr. Anthony Catalano P.h. D. speak. Take advantage now as this is the only time this opportunity will be available until sometime in the Fall.
item.name: Dr. Anthony Catalano, P.h.D. Keynote Speaker
